About Me

Strategy is powerful.


It’s the force that transforms ideas into programs that drive growth and engage audiences. Many talk about strategy—I focus on building initiatives that deliver real impact.

HEY, I’M HAZEL!

With experience across diverse industries, from Tech to international marketing, I specialize in providing tactic approach and implementing data-driven that bridge strategy with real-world impact.

My work spans digital analytics, cross-functional collaboration, and logistics coordination, all with a focus on innovation and measurable growth. I thrive in dynamic, fast-paced environments, where my adaptability, problem-solving skills, and global team communication abilities drive successful outcomes.
